      <title>施洛斯坦称美联储对市场的重要性正在下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-22/schlosstein-says-fed-becoming-less-important-to-markets-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Evercore 名誉主席 Ralph Schlosstein 讨论了特朗普政府领导下的金融市场前景。在“彭博社收盘”节目中，Schlosstein 还评论了人工智能对市场的影响以及他认为的股票风险。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-22/schlosstein-says-fed-becoming-less-important-to-markets-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 21:08:51 GMT</pubDate>
